    pulse_width = generate_data_point(material, thickness)[2]

    data_points.append([material, thickness, pulse_width, energy, spot_size, intensity, power, cutoff_energy])

df = pd.DataFrame(data, columns=['target_material', 'target_thickness', 'pulse_width', 'energy', 'spot_size', 'intensity', 'power', 'cutoff_energy'])
print(df)
